query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, p.id as price_id, p.apiId, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice, p.currency 
FROM services s 
JOIN prices p ON s.id = p.serviceId 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Outros%' AND p.apiId = 2 
LIMIT 5;
